---
source: crates/markdown-neuraxis-syntax/src/lib.rs
expression: "insta_format_tree(&tree, 0)"
---
ROOT@0..27
  THEMATIC_BREAK@0..4
    DASH@0..1 "-"
    DASH@1..2 "-"
    DASH@2..3 "-"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\\n"
  PARAGRAPH@4..27
    TEXT@4..9 "title"
    COLON@9..10 ":"
    WHITESPACE@10..11 " "
    TEXT@11..15 "Test"
    NEWLINE@15..16 "\\n"
    TEXT@16..18 "no"
    WHITESPACE@18..19 " "
    TEXT@19..26 "closing"
    NEWLINE@26..27 "\\n"
